Nottinghamshire, England October 1983\. Colette Aram was a 16 year old trainee hairdresser when she made the 10 minute walk to see her boyfriend one Sunday night. But she never arrived.&#13;
&#13;
In this episode of the UK True Crime Weekly Podcast we examine what happened to Colette and the brave fight for justice fought by her family.&#13;
